sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cashier
    participant POS as POS System
    participant I as Inventory
    participant P as PaymentProcessor
    participant R as ReceiptPrinter
    
    C->>POS: Start New Sale
    POS-->>C: Sale Created
    
    loop For Each Item
        C->>POS: Scan Product
        POS->>I: Check Stock Availability
        I-->>POS: Stock Available
        POS->>POS: Add to Cart
        POS-->>C: Update Display
    end
    
    C->>POS: Complete Sale
    POS->>POS: Calculate Total
    POS-->>C: Display Total
    
    C->>POS: Process Payment
    POS->>P: Authorize Payment
    P-->>POS: Payment Approved
    POS->>I: Update Inventory
    POS->>R: Print Receipt
    POS-->>C: Sale Complete
